pip install requests

URL FORMAT:
Set base_url to: https://your-server.com/MicroStrategyLibrarySTD
Do NOT include /api — the script appends that in every call automatically.

LOGIN MODE:
loginMode 1  = Standard (username/password)
loginMode 8  = Windows / Network (NTLM)
loginMode 16 = LDAP
Update LOGIN_MODE below to match your environment.

USAGE:

